data.text:
To test the camera, you can use Mech-Eye Viewer. Here are the steps:

1. Click on Start Mech-Eye Viewer in Mech-Center.
2. Connect to the camera by either double-clicking the camera IP on the left or clicking on the camera IP and then clicking on Connect Camera in the bottom center.
3. After connecting successfully, you will enter the camera viewer interface.
4. Click on Continuous Scan to keep capturing images, or click Scan Once to capture one image at a time.
5. If the camera can capture images correctly, click on Stop.
